OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FZoe Watts and Amanda Stanhope were
OL,7,Fboth abused by their former partners
OL,8,Fwhile unconscious. ITV News has
OL,9,Fbrought them together for the first
OL,10,Ftime as they launch a campaign they
OL,11,Fsay is long overdue.
OL,13,FThis report by ITV News Correspondent
OL,14,FSejal Karia contains details you may
OL,15,Ffind distressing
OL,17,FAdditional reporting by ITV Senior
OL,18,FProducers Eleanor Gregory and Louisa
OL,19,FFelton
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
