OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FThey had never met in person, but
OL,7,Fshare the same story.
OL,9,FOn Wednesday, Zoe Watts and Amanda
OL,10,FStanhope came face-to-face for the
OL,11,Ffirst time. They are two women whose
OL,12,Flives have been shattered by the men
OL,13,Fthey trusted most, and who have now
OL,14,Ffound in each other a reason to fight
OL,15,Fback.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
