PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FTogether they are launching
OL,7,F_EndEyeCheck, a survivor-led campaign
OL,8,Ftargeting the legal loopholes they say
OL,9,Fallow men to drug, rape and film their
OL,10,Fpartners - and to share that material
OL,11,Fonline, in networks where such abuse
OL,12,Fis not just hidden, but glorified,
OL,13,Fpromoted and traded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
