PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FAmanda's story follows a similarly
OL,7,Fdevastating pattern. For five years
OL,8,Fshe endured coercive control and
OL,9,Ftorment at the hands of the man that
OL,10,Fclaimed to love her.
OL,12,FShe was medicating heavily just to
OL,13,Fcope with the abuse by taking
OL,14,Fantidepressants. Sometimes, she would
OL,15,Fwake up bruised, disoriented and in
OL,16,Fdifferent clothes, with no memory of
OL,17,Fwhat had happened to her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FWhen she confronted her partner, he
OL,7,Ftold her she was imagining it - that
OL,8,Fshe was confused, unstable, and on too
OL,9,Fmuch medication. He was eventually
OL,10,Fcharged with multiple counts of rape
OL,11,Fand sexual assault. He took his own
OL,12,Flife before the case could reach court.
OL,14,FWhat unites both women - beyond the
OL,15,Fnature of their abuse - is the silence
OL,16,Fthat surrounded it. Neither knew, for
OL,17,Fyears, what was being done to them.
OL,18,FAnd that, they say, is precisely the
OL,19,Fpoint.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
