OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FCentral to the campaign is a term most
OL,7,Fpeople will never have encountered:
OL,8,Fthe "eye check." It describes a
OL,9,Fspecific act - deliberate and filmed -
OL,10,Fin which a perpetrator pulls back the
OL,11,Feyelid of a victim who is unconscious
OL,12,For incapacitated.
OL,14,FIt is a way of confirming their
OL,15,Fcomplete helplessness.
OL,26,@pD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
