OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FThe campaign is calling for new
OL,7,Flegislation to make the creation,
OL,8,Fpossession and distribution of such
OL,9,Fmaterial a specific criminal offence,
OL,10,Fand for online platforms to be held
OL,11,Flegally accountable for hosting it.
OL,13,FAlongside that, Zoe and Amanda want to
OL,14,Fraise funds to build an international
OL,15,Fsupport network for survivors, many of
OL,16,Fwhom may not yet know they are
OL,17,Fsurvivors at all.
OL,19,FNeither woman might be here were it
OL,20,Fnot for Gisele Pelicot.
OL,26,@|D@Lqr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
