OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FIf you want to make contact with our
OL,7,Fteam, please email
OL,8,Finvestigations@itv.com.
OL,10,FThe Pelicot case was not an anomaly.
OL,12,FIn the UK, in February, a man admitted
OL,13,Fto raping and sexually assaulting his
OL,14,Fthen wife. Separately, later this year
OL,15,Fa trial is provisionally due to start
OL,16,Fin Manchester after another man denied
OL,17,Fdrugging his wife for sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
