PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FFor Zoe and Amanda, Wednesday's
OL,7,Fmeeting is the beginning of something
OL,8,Flarger - a push to move the
OL,9,Fconversation out of courtrooms and
OL,10,Finto law, into classrooms, into the
OL,11,Fawareness of every person who has
OL,12,Fnever thought they needed to worry
OL,13,Fabout the person sleeping beside them.
OL,15,FZoe and Amanda told ITV News that they
OL,16,Fhave been contacted by hundreds of
OL,17,Fwomen from all over the world - from
OL,18,FMexico, Canada, the US, Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
