CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778119410
OL,3,CSurvivors launch campaign to end
OL,4,Csexual abuse of unconscious women
OL,6,FThey are determined that other women
OL,7,Fshould not have to find out the same
OL,8,Fway they did. And they want their
OL,9,Fcampaign to achieve lasting change.
OL,11,F_EndEyeCheck has now launched at
OL,12,Fendeyecheck.org.
OL,14,FBoth Zoe Watts and Amanda Stanhope
OL,15,Fhave waived their right to anonymity.
OL,17,FIf you, or someone you know, has been
OL,18,Fa victim of rape of sexual violence,
OL,19,Fthere is support out there to help:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
